/*************************************************
 * End of normal operational data
 *
 *  CANID from 1400 – 1499 are non publishable
 * They are reserved for internal use on any specific
 * device.  Look at photon.h for GDI device use
 *
 *  CANID from 1500-2047 are reserved by neutron
 * for pipes.
 * Pipe 0 is always the console pipe
 * Pipe 2 is a protobuf pipe for neutron
 *
 * Devices can support up to 16 services
 * There can be up to 16 devices on a CanFly bus
 */
